<H1> 2dx </H1>
<b>Version:</b>@2dx_VERSION_MAJOR@.@2dx_VERSION_MINOR@.@2dx_VERSION_PATCH@<br>
<p></p>
<b>License and Availability:</b><br>
 2dx is released under the <a href="http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html">GNU-GPL</a>, and is available on <a href="http://2dx.org/download/2dx-software">2dx.org</a>. <BR>
It runs natively on Mac OSX and Linux/X11 (Linux, and other Unix variants).
